longBusinessSummary: Quality Power Electrical Equipments Limited provides power products and solutions for power generation, transmission, distribution, and automation sectors. Its power products include reactors, line traps, transformers, instrument transformers, line tuners, metal enclosed capacitor banks, and composites; and power quality systems comprise static VAR compensators, harmonic filters, capacitor banks, shunt reactors, and static synchronous compensators. The company also offers converters and reactive power compensation systems. It serves power utilities, power industries, and renewable energy entities. Quality Power Electrical Equipments Limited was incorporated in 2001 and is based in Sangli, India.
